      "writtenOn": "2019-11-18T17:40:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "A few thoughts in no particular order:\n\n- Should all references to endpoints in tests under $SKIA_INFRA_ROOT/golden/modules be constants as well?\n\n- I\u0027m not sure this aids with readability, and since this endpoint does not take any parameters, changing it should be a simple find/replace operation. What do you think?\n\n- (Tangentially related, but worth mentioning) At some point we\u0027ll have integration tests in place, which should break if e.g. the endpoint referenced in the component or its corresponding unit test changes with respect to the skiacorrectness binary.",
